articles.author: Lim Hui Jie
articles.title: Japan October exports massively beat estimates on robust growth in shipments to Asia and Europe - CNBC
articles.description: Exports grew 3.6% year on year compared with expectations of a 1.1% growth by economists polled by Reuters.
articles.content:
Japan's exports in October massively beat expectations, government data on Friday showed, as shipments to Europe and Asia saw robust growth.
